item.description:
Join us as the Metro West YP group migrates to Providence for dinner at Uno's Chicago Grill inside the Providence Place Mall, followed by a night of fun at Dave and Busters. Also located inside the Providence Place Mall (top floor, above the food court), Dave and Busters offers full bar and tons of games.

We will meet for dinner at 7pm at Uno's Chicago Grill, then we will head upstairs to Dave and Busters. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000.

Uno's is located on the Francis Street side of the mall and is accessed via Level C cityside.

This event is also posted on the Social Fun meet up site. Please join us for a fun evening!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside Uno. If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Dinner at Uno's, then Drinks, Games and Fun at Dave and Busters, Providence
